AirLines Delay Causes Exploration¶

By Hosam Elbakry¶

The data we have here -from Udacity datasets options- is airlines delay causes from 2017 till 2020 and contains 22 column and 69522 record or row through the project we will start to understand the dataset variables and carryout the necessary wrangling/cleaning and then figure out which variables worthy to be concluded in our analysis. The insights we are trying to inspect here for example what is the main cause of delay, what is the best time for travel, is the destination affect on delay.

In [11]:
base_color = sns.color_palette()[0] # Indentify the first color from the tuple list of colors
In [12]:
# The below function will help throughtout this project , as we have to mention X - lable , y-lable , 
# title each and every time we plot any graph for clear understanding .
def lables_name(x , y = None):
    plt.xlabel(x)
    plt.ylabel(y)
    if(y == None):
        plt.title(f' {x} Distribution');
    else:
        plt.title(f' {x} and {y} Distribution')
